import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { MatDialog } from '@angular/material/dialog'; import { DailogLoginComponent } from '../dailog-login/dailog-login.component'; import { DailogSignupComponent } from '../dailog-signup/dailog-signup.component'; import { MyserviceService } from '../myservice.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-biryani-bay', templateUrl: './biryani-bay.component.html', styleUrls: ['./biryani-bay.component.css'] }) export class BiryaniBayComponent { login: any; user: any; userget: any; constructor(public dialog: MatDialog, private service: MyserviceService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.service.datachangeobservable.subscribe((d) => (this.login = d)); this.user = localStorage.getItem('Name') const user1 = this.user.replaceAll('"', ' ') this.userget = user1 } openDialog() { this.dialog.open(DailogLoginComponent); } opensignupDialog() { this.dialog.open(DailogSignupComponent); } }
